table abc_extra67.update_get_cache_checks:
  description: "abc update_abstractmethods co_varnames and get_cache_token class checks in abcmore67 namespace — wave 238 theme: update_abstractmethods co_varnames + get_cache_token class identity; update_abstractmethods.__code__.co_varnames.__class__.__name__=='tuple' (co_varnames is always a tuple in CPython); get_cache_token.__class__.__name__=='builtin_function_or_method' (get_cache_token is from _abc C extension); NEW in extra67: first co_varnames type check for update_abstractmethods and class name check for get_cache_token in the abcmore67 namespace; verified with Python 3.14.3"
  kind: python_call_eq
  category: code
  id_prefix: abcmore67b

  columns: [id, function, args, expected, description]
  rows:
    - [update_varnames_cls,  update_abstractmethods.__code__.co_varnames.__class__.__name__.__eq__, ["tuple"],                    true, "update_abstractmethods.__code__.co_varnames.__class__.__name__ == 'tuple' — co_varnames is always a tuple in CPython; update_abstractmethods.__code__.co_varnames.__class__.__name__ is 'tuple'; NEW in extra67: first co_varnames type check for update_abstractmethods in the abcmore67 namespace; verified with Python 3.14.3"]
    - [gct_class_name,       get_cache_token.__class__.__name__.__eq__,                             ["builtin_function_or_method"], true, "get_cache_token.__class__.__name__ == 'builtin_function_or_method' — abc.get_cache_token is implemented in the _abc C extension module; its __class__.__name__ is 'builtin_function_or_method'; NEW in extra67: first __class__.__name__.__eq__ check for get_cache_token in the abcmore67 namespace; verified with Python 3.14.3"]

