table abc_extra67.abstractproperty_dict:
  description: "abc abstractproperty.__dict__.__class__.__name__ check in abcmore67 namespace — wave 238 theme: abstractproperty __dict__ type identity; abstractproperty.__dict__.__class__.__name__=='mappingproxy' (Python class __dict__ is always a mappingproxy); NEW in extra67: first __dict__.__class__.__name__ check for abstractproperty in the abcmore67 namespace; verified with Python 3.14.3"
