    - [absprop_dict_cls, abstractproperty.__dict__.__class__.__name__.__eq__, ["mappingproxy"], true, "abstractproperty.__dict__.__class__.__name__ == 'mappingproxy' — Python class __dict__ is always a mappingproxy; abc.abstractproperty.__dict__.__class__.__name__ is 'mappingproxy'; NEW in extra67: first __dict__.__class__.__name__.__eq__('mappingproxy') check for abstractproperty in the abcmore67 namespace; verified with Python 3.14.3"]

